  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section id="how" class="bg-white py-12">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Kaise kaam karta hai</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600">Raiku slot reservation, transaction scheduling aur validator coordination ko combine karta hai taaki inclusion predictable ho. Yahan simplified flow:</p>

      <ol class="mt-6 space-y-4 list-decimal pl-6 text-gray-700">
        <li><strong>Reserve:</strong> Builder reserve karta hai blockspace via a small on-chain or off-chain commitment.</li>
        <li><strong>Coordinate:</strong> Validators aur relayers coordinate karte hain to include the reserved tx in the chosen slot.</li>
        <li><strong>Execute & Confirm:</strong> Tx gets included with proof of inclusion and guaranteed execution ordering.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

